                <note rend="inline" type="source">721.23 Repatriates/4: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Peru</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dearing</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-02-24T11:00:00-05:00"
                            >February 24, 1933—11 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>40. Your 96, February 21, midnight, and 99 February 23, 10 a.m. Department
                    believes it inadvisable for you or the Department to take any initiative in this
                    matter.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
